title: Wolf Designs Windsor Module 2.5 Automatic Watch Winder
description:
Video transcript: The Viceroy Collection of watch winders is available with or without additional watch storage. The Viceroy Triple 2.7 Watch Winder with storage winds up to three watches and houses up to five more in its top compartment.

These winders are finished with a supple black pebble textured material on the outside, a sliver textured faceplate, and shiny chromed hardware.
